info.author: Dominik Traxl
info.name: DeepGraph
info.summary: DeepGraph is an efficient, general-purpose data analysis Python package. Based on pandas DataFrames, it provides the means to analyze data via graph theory (a.k.a. networks).

info.author: Dominik Traxl
classifiers: Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Python Modules
info.name: DeepGraph
info.summary: DeepGraph is a scalable, general-purpose data analysis package. It implements a network representation based on pandas DataFrames and provides methods to construct, partition and plot graphs, to interface with popular network packages and more.
